name: Agent
line: What's up Rick!

name: Rick
line: Morty!

name: Agent
line: Rick!

name: Rick
line: I told ya not to invite this mummified motherfucker back!

name: Agent
line: Hey, it's fine. He's just a phantom train conductor. You don't really have to worry about him.

name: Rick
line: That's it, Rick! I'm taking the wheel!

name: Agent
line: Whoa, whoa! Whoa! Whoooooaaaa! Who's got it better, Morty?

name: Rick
line: Who's got the shit on his face?

name: Agent
line: What the hell is that, Frank?

name: Rick
line: It's a device, Morty! It's a chemical that makes your brain secrete what's in your food. If you put it in your ear, you'll die.

name: Agent
line: What's the chemical thing?

name: Rick
line: Frank's got a chemical thing going on him that he's trying to use to kill us! It might be something we could put in our food, Morty.

name: Agent
line: Ugh, Frank.

name: Rick
line: It'll do, Frank!

name: Agent
line: Ugghh!

name: Rick
line: It won't do, Morty, it won't!

name: Agent
line: Don't worry about Frank. He'll be fine.

name: Rick
line: Oh, Frank, I'm sorry. I know you're worried about me. I'm a little worried about you.

name: Agent
line: Whoopsie! Oh, my God! Oh! Oh.

name: Rick
line: No, Frank is dying.

name: Agent
line: Yeah, Frank's worried about us.
